						<p class="newsHeader">
							Old forums days numbered
							Thursday, February 19, 2004 - 1:04:06 AM
						</p>
						<p class="newsBody">
							<P>The old forums are on the way out....&nbsp; I don`t have a specific date in mind yet, its basically going to depend on when I get the new forums to a point where I consider the features to be equal, which really isnt that far off.&nbsp; Maybe another couple weeks, as I will probably only get work on the forums on the weekends when i have some spare time.&nbsp; </P>
<P>I know I said that I might allow the old forums to continue to run, but with both running, it`s a big waste of server resources.&nbsp;Now that guilds are really starting to use the new forums, I am seeing that it`s just not going to workout with both forums running.&nbsp; Also, the old forums are starting to act up again with that dumb connection warning.... </P>
<P>I figure I would mention it now, to give those using the old forums a few weeks to let it sink in.... some of the guilds have already started using the new forums.&nbsp; Some are continuing to use them until I turn them off... which is fine.&nbsp; Like I said, I won`t force anyone until the new forums have all the features I want, and they are working 100%.</P>
						</p>
					
